<h1 id="toc4"><span>What this is</span></h1>
<p>A component that applies the <a href="http://scptestwiki.wikidot.com/">Black Highlighter</a> theme to your article.</p>
<p>This component will apply a stable version of the Black Highlighter theme, but it might break sometimes as it's updated.</p>
<h1 id="toc5"><span>Reporting problems</span></h1>
<p>If you've got a Github account, create an Issue <a href="https://github.com/Nu-SCPTheme/Black-Highlighter/issues">here</a> detailing your problem (whether it's technical, or aesthetic, or whatever).</p>
<p>If you don't have a Github account, or if you'd prefer to discuss your issues with someone directly, either join the <tt>#black-highlighter</tt> channel on SynIRC, or send a PM to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404096); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608535860" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404096); return false;">Woedenaz</a></span> or <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608535860" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span>.</p>
